Package: itscausal
Title: Interrupted Time Series for Causal Estimation
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Aurelien", "Sallin", , "aurelien.sallin@protonmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "YOUR-ORCID-ID"))
Description: This package performs single- and multiple-steps forecasting for
    estimating causal effects using time series. It relies on machine learning 
    methods for prediction with crossfitting and ensemble learning.
